import React, { useState } from 'react'; import axios from '../commons/axios'; const AddCat = () => { const [cat, setCat] = useState({ name: '', breed: '', age: '', description: '', location: '', image: '', ageUnit: 'Year' }); const handleChange = e => { setCat({ ...cat, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; const handleSubmit = e => { e.preventDefault(); axios.post('/add-cat', cat) .then(response => { console.log(response.data); }) .catch(error => { console.error('There was an error!', error); }); }; return (
); }; export default AddCat;
